Covid ASEAN Dataset

covid_asean_df.Rd

This is dataset used for producing covid ASEAN shiny dashboard. The dataset contains covid-19 cases data from Indonesia, Malaysia, Philippines, Singapore and Thailand.

covid_asean_df

Format

a tibble with 203 rows and 53 columns.

References

Gassen, Joachim. 2020. Tidycovid19: Download, Tidy and Visualize Covid-19 Related Data. (Tidycovid19)
